.TH "ORG.BLUEZ.THERMOMETERMANAGER" "5" "July 2011" "BlueZ" "Linux System Administration"
.SH NAME
org.bluez.ThermometerManager \- BlueZ D-Bus Health ThermometerManager API documentation
.SH INTERFACE
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B Service
org.bluez
.TP
.B Interface
org.bluez.ThermometerManager1
.TP
.B Object path
[variable prefix]/{hci0,hci1,...}
.UNINDENT
.SS Methods
.SS void RegisterWatcher(object agent)
.sp
Registers a watcher to monitor scanned measurements.
This agent will be notified about final temperature
measurements.
.sp
Possible Errors:
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B org.bluez.Error.InvalidArguments
.UNINDENT
.SS void UnregisterWatcher(object agent)
.sp
Unregisters a watcher.
.SS void EnableIntermediateMeasurement(object agent)
.sp
Enables intermediate measurement notifications
for this agent. Intermediate measurements will
be enabled only for thermometers which support it.
.sp
Possible Errors:
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B org.bluez.Error.InvalidArguments
.UNINDENT
.SS void DisableIntermediateMeasurement(object agent)
.sp
Disables intermediate measurement notifications
for this agent. It will disable notifications in
thermometers when the last agent removes the
watcher for intermediate measurements.
.sp
Possible Errors:
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B org.bluez.Error.InvalidArguments
.TP
.B org.bluez.Error.NotFound
